Paper: hep-th/9307117

Date: 1993-07-19

Title: Canonical Quantisation in n.A=0 gauges

Authors: P V Landshoff and P van Nieuwenhuizen

Comments: 7 pages, DAMTP 93-33, ITP-SB-93-38

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D50 (1994) 4157-4161

We give a unified derivation of the propagator in the gauges $n.A=0$ for$n^2$ timelike, spacelike or lightlike. We discuss the physical states andother physical questions.